  - Title: Srimad Bhagavatam
    Location: XI xiii
Tags:
  - Life-Love=Prayer-Meditation-Contemplation=Help Through Prayer
  - 57
  - Combat-Action=Orthodoxy-Ritual-Method
---
If the yogi, being deluded, makes mistakes in life, he should bum
away his sins and impurities by prayer and meditation. This yoga of
prayer and meditation is the only way of atonement.
